        public BSR xorM(BSR sr)
        Mutable XORs bitwise this object with the given ShiftReg and returns this object. If both ShiftRegs don't have equal size, then null will be returned. Therefore, it's the responsibility of the caller of this method to decide how they want to pad (right or left) the smaller object.
